{"tid":208612,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人氣管敏感 做親激烈運動都氣喘？","createTime":"2017-04-19T15:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T08:12:14.000Z","uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99bcc4609d1f60adf578b236970a8a76531349cd","tid":208612,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"好想知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個個陣踢波跑一陣就會起痰 氣喘<br />\n個陣又唔知咩事 以為係自己做得唔夠運動<br />\n大少少(高中)<br />\n開始會慢跑 氣喘有改善左少少<br />\n但係唔知點解 踢波跑上跑落 個種跑法就好容易起痰<br />\n有次感冒咳得太勢利 咳到嘔咁濟<br />\n醫生話係氣管敏感<br />\n食左藥好返之後<br />\n做返運動都會起痰<br />\n到底點樣可以根治<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee403ac3185ac2f32a95956a3b0159a47da05df0","tid":208612,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"我行樓梯、斜路、跑步都好易扯蝦<br />\n以為自己廢西 係咪同你一樣氣管敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fbba1b2caa7e8638b22a421d00599d50e2cdcb","tid":208612,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"我冬天會喘得特別犀利，要吸哮喘藥，但夏天又無事"},{"pid":"d4f5ef1be9941ea6724e2d10173353330695259b","tid":208612,"uid":77194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"試下用腹式呼吸 <br />\n同埋吸氣嗰陣用鼻吸大啖啲，呼氣就用口慢慢呼出黎"},{"pid":"f8f24c0bc0966951c6f80d94dbccc48a406f323e","tid":208612,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"香港空氣太差，去瑞士山區一排就冇事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸：半9up"},{"pid":"06a98976da28ca572c6f5a145118a64aaa72f6c3","tid":208612,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我行樓梯、斜路、跑步都好易扯蝦<br />\n以為自己廢西 係咪同你一樣氣管敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行樓梯我都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係踢波跑上跑落 要衝刺 踢幾分鐘就起痰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ff71402bcbd7da2971a1512ac3221a8cb1c10f","tid":208612,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下用腹式呼吸 <br />\n同埋吸氣嗰陣用鼻吸大啖啲，呼氣就用口慢慢呼出黎</blockquote><br />\n下次跑步試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75809d4d892ab647eb7bb94f73a0a701c2e055f","tid":208612,"uid":66,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"同你症狀差唔多<br />\n但我係慢性氣管炎<br />\n屋企人有煲過鱷魚肉比我飲<br />\n個排冇咁容易扯蝦<br />\n但好貴<br />\n飲左排就冇再煲<br />\n之後有同事知我有氣管炎<br />\n佢話游水可以改善到<br />\n但我未去實踐<br />\n太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1000efae941843d7177bed1ada368c12cf005b3","tid":208612,"uid":22135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"我都有<br />\n打籃球來回跑太急就出事<br />\n要慢跑熱好身就無問題<br />\n出左事就好難回氣<br />\n要吸兩啖綠色支氣就順好多"},{"pid":"ff498700015748b3ef5616bf2e9d302ace1a783f","tid":208612,"uid":22135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你症狀差唔多<br />\n但我係慢性氣管炎<br />\n屋企人有煲過鱷魚肉比我飲<br />\n個排冇咁容易扯蝦<br />\n但好貴<br />\n飲左排就冇再煲<br />\n之後有同事知我有氣管炎<br />\n佢話游水可以改善到<br />\n但我未去實踐<br />\n太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n游水個排的確好左，不過都係懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5950b894f9126255cdf7862fd48de7cc37d1cf7","tid":208612,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:03:29.000Z","msg":"我跑步後改善了氣喘/哮喘，一星期抽一兩天跑<br />\n鱷魚肉湯對我冇乜效用，<br />\n試過針炙中藥對哮喘亦冇乜效（可能同醫生唔夾）"},{"pid":"2a3957ffae827c1b28428fb2f0904eb5075cfe22","tid":208612,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:04:46.000Z","msg":"做完激烈運動都唔氣喘, 係咩玩法 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4b8c1892809466296053dab96c65b3b0bc8115","tid":208612,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"我自己有 關轉天氣事 同屋企大唔大塵事"},{"pid":"7e2cffc2064bf66a090cfddb212376bd42924324","tid":208612,"uid":94484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你症狀差唔多<br />\n但我係慢性氣管炎<br />\n屋企人有煲過鱷魚肉比我飲<br />\n個排冇咁容易扯蝦<br />\n但好貴<br />\n飲左排就冇再煲<br />\n之後有同事知我有氣管炎<br />\n佢話游水可以改善到<br />\n但我未去實踐<br />\n太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個果時一到冬天就喘<br />\n好似抖唔到氣咁<br />\n每次都要去醫務所吸氣<br />\n之後屋企煲鱷魚肉飲就斷左尾"},{"pid":"fc79b4e2c2b1594bd49d6de7097eb6a21598e114","tid":208612,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"做脫敏治療"},{"pid":"c68a7e00f69995b4ad6499c0ab76a2d06d4e3d5e","tid":208612,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你症狀差唔多<br />\n但我係慢性氣管炎<br />\n屋企人有煲過鱷魚肉比我飲<br />\n個排冇咁容易扯蝦<br />\n但好貴<br />\n飲左排就冇再煲<br />\n之後有同事知我有氣管炎<br />\n佢話游水可以改善到<br />\n但我未去實踐<br />\n太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n游水個排的確好左，不過都係懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n游水學好耐都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓練池游到一半又唔知點透氣@@"},{"pid":"eccd00c40702948c5c1efaa660ffb1709b2cdaa8","tid":208612,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"笑得太癲容易喘 唱K成日起痰"},{"pid":"fea8bfcccfa0815cbe8d7a1eabd5ef8838529f3f","tid":208612,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"人多都覺得透唔到氣"}]}